OpenU IL Block Users Online - Advanced
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

----------------------------------------------------
Description
----------------------------------------------------

Enclosed is an improved version of the Moodle "Users Online" block. In this version only users
who are members of the same course will see each other.


----------------------------------------------------
Installation Information
----------------------------------------------------

1. Copy "online_users_advanced" directory to moodle/block.
2. In Moodle log-in as admin and go to the notifications page (in the Site Administration block).
3. The installation will be automatic.


----------------------------------------------------
Notes
----------------------------------------------------

There currently is a bug that the admin cannot see anyone in this block.


